item.title: Thoughtworks TWinnoFest 3.0
item.description: The TWiinoFest 3.0 Innovation Lab’s at Thoughtworks comes 3rd edition of iFest - a month long hackathon in remote working environment, distributed across cities. I got opportunity to participate in Finale as a judge. I was amazed to see the verity of idea. All the ideas were great and it was so hard to compare them. Ideas were touching were reflecting the Thougthworks culture, use technology to solve challenges society is facing.
